<!--
THE EVIDENCE - How long these APIs have existed:

window.open() 
  First appeared: Netscape Navigator 2.0 - December 1995 (30 YEARS OLD)

localStorage
  First appeared: HTML5 spec - Late 2000s (~2009) (16 YEARS OLD)

Fullscreen API
  First appeared: ~2011-2012 (Firefox 10 in 2012) (13 YEARS OLD)

screen.width / screen.height
  First appeared: Original JavaScript - 1995 (30 YEARS OLD)

Google's Window Management API: Started 2018, Shipped 2022 (4 years)

The APIs existed for DECADES. They chose complexity anyway.
-->

